<br>
The healer then has to heal them which aggro's the healer and blows a ton of mana.<br>
<br>
If you get a pack of mobs and the bard isn't going to CC, they'd almost be more useful doing straight melee or ( you guessed it ) sitting their butts down and playing c2 song.  <br>
<br>
For god sakes don't play a AE heal song when you have 3-4 live mobs and the tank is trying to maintain aggro of all of them.<br>
<br>
